:0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:57:16.000Z","msg":"除咗唔再捐錢俾無國界醫生之外，我哋可以做多樣野<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1738004\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1738004</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n#SOSHK"},{"pid":"6a8d2c5a424866e2d6ef888c7f92e44fcb89838c","tid":1738270,"uid":149877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:58:42.000Z","msg":"唔會難cut過有線掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66cefc1603270bd43488e1567f79065b82be1c78","tid":1738270,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:59:37.000Z","msg":"做乞衣仲咁撚惡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申由細到大都覺得自動轉帳捐錢係好on9既"},{"pid":"bfd47def27f98babad577bfd5ff55506ed9ea410","tid":1738270,"uid":294068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:06:55.000Z","msg":"停左銀行個授權書未得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f19c0d44bbee7dab5406650a0d6f53cc136d2d73","tid":1738270,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:34:40.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">《無國界醫生》取消每月捐款通知表格</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/11/19/VIdm6S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F11%2F19%2FVIdm6S.jpg&h=e0d8c459&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://msf.hk/sites/hong-kong/files/Cancellation%20Form.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmsf.hk%2Fsites%2Fhong-kong%2Ffiles%2FCancellation%2520Form.pdf&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4MqvjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=28d71949\" target=\"_blank\">https://msf.hk/sites/hong-kong/files/Cancellation%20Form.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>填妥後以電郵傳送到無國界醫生 (香港) 捐款事務部即可</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<code>donation@hongkong.msf.org</code>"},{"pid":"f08f3b1656b4214cf3b2202a3247ef9a6924cd6f","tid":1738270,"uid":322689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfd47def27f98babad577bfd5ff55506ed9ea410","tid":1738270,"uid":294068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:06:55.000Z","msg":"停左銀行個授權書未得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T13:52:13.000Z","msg":"無恥界醫生熱線已廢，想cut捐款但又打唔通hotline，可以直接打去銀行或者網上銀行自己cut，我以HSBC為例，做法係：<br />\n<br />\n1. 先登入HSBC網上理財（一定要電腦版，電話app不能）<br />\n2. 然後喺 &quot;我的銀行&quot; 欄目下揀 &quot;自動轉賬 &quot;<br />\n3. 揀 &quot;管理自動轉賬&quot;，然後就會見到你每月要轉賬嘅項目<br />\n4. 揀返 &quot;Medecins Sans F HK L&quot;，然後 &quot;刪除指示&quot; 再確認<br />\n<br />\n咁就可以成功cut捐款，但我唔知其他銀行網上理財係咪一樣，大家即管試吓！<br />\n<br />\n唔捐都唔夠，要攞返之前捐過嘅錢！方法如下：<br />\n可以打上card centre要求charge back返晒之前所有捐款<br />\nchargeback除咗攞返錢，商戶係要食好貴手續費<br />\n(chargeback 只限 credit card）"}]}